THE GAME
--------

  'Coulisso' is a Workbench game where you move bars, following
diagonal path sections, so they are placed on the same space. When
2 bars are on the same path section, these 'explode' and the path
section, where the bars were located, will become a 'hole', which
will be impassable thereafter...

  Complete each game board with the least amount of moves... and
above all, avoid isolating bars!

  Have fun!

